fields.name: EffectiveNoProxy
fields.description: A read-only list of all endpoints for which traffic should not be sent to the proxy. This list is a superset of noProxy and values injected by AKS.

fields.name: HTTPProxy
fields.description: The HTTP proxy server endpoint to use.

fields.name: HTTPSProxy
fields.description: The HTTPS proxy server endpoint to use.

fields.name: NoProxy
fields.description: The endpoints that should not go through proxy.

fields.name: TrustedCa
fields.description: Alternative CA cert to use for connecting to proxy servers.
